magicianstowerthingstokill.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=61.topic&index=11>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Where to hunt</span><hr size=1> Get ye to Kunark.  Lake of Ill Omen does not green out until 30, then move to the Frontier Mountains.  That will see you easily to 35.  From there, head to the Overthere.  Get you to mid 40's.  You can solo all three of these spots easily (group is better for Overthere, but you could solo).<br>
<br>
My Opinions Only, your mileage may vary. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> Fuzze</span><br> <span class=usertitle>Unregistered User</span><br>   <font color=#333333>(8/17/00 6:00:13 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerthingstokill.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=61.topic&index=12>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Where to hunt</span><hr size=1> Just for the record i wasnt bashing ...that sentence 'Druids and necro's can solo better' was probably prevalent in my head when writing that..anyway why post leveling info on where to go? thats what the Where to hunt forums are for =) <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/ulaelaran.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Laelaran</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>   <font color=#333333>(8/21/00 9:36:11 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerthingstokill.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=61.topic&index=13>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Magicians? SOLO?</span><hr size=1> Best place to solo that i know of when you get to around 32-33 and you dont mind taking a faction hit, would be the bard in South Karana.  Took me 3 days to get from 33-38 there.  Fast spawn (approx 7 mins) he's a lvl 33 and hits a lot, so use your Damage shield, and nuke away.  By the time your 35 you own him.<br>
<br>
Laelaran Fyrestaff<br>
53rd Elementalist<br>
The Comapanions<br>
